title: Bollywood Showstoppers 2013
description:
Flex FX returns in spectacular fashion with a new musical dance extravaganza to bring you Bollywood like you’ve never seen it before with Bollywood Showstoppers at The O2 on Sunday 7 April 2013.

The Bollywood Showstoppers include the beautiful Bollywood icon BIPASHA BASU, the dancing queen MALAIKA ARORA KHAN, the sensational SHAAN and the rockstar ATIF ASLAM. All performing live and exclusive and supported by the UK’s most popular Bollywood dancers BOLLY FLEX. For more information visit www.bollywoodshowstoppers.com
